data.title: Non Engg Institute
data.meta_description: Non Engg Institute - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document contains a list of 11 universities, colleges, and institutions located in West Bengal affiliated with the Calcutta University. It includes the name of each institution, its address, contact person, their email and phone number. The institutions cover various districts of West Bengal like Kolkata, Howrah, Paschim Medinipur.
